, and Suni Lee during their on-mat routines.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999358806, \"rank\": 6.41167519574096e-11, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999319570657, \"rank\": 6.622514510990259e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}, {\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.999699355330322, \"rank\": 0.0003007347586784995, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leanne_Battersby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leanne\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leanne_Battersby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leanne_Battersby\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Roberson\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 4.213528610542108e-12, \"text\": \"Roberson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Roberson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Roberson\"}, {\"begin\": 957, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\":