": 0.999746754717797, \"rank\": 0.00016045294068844552, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every crystal\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"the garments\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the shimmering additives are inspired by old Hollywood glitz and the red, white, and blue hues are meant to motivate patriotic spirit, pearl detailing will also be incorporated as an ode to the \\\"City of Love.\\\"\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999828282854, \"rank\": 1.717158386197176e-08, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shimmering additives\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"the red, white, and blue hues\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"patriotic spirit\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"pearl\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"an ode\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"City\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"Love\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a July 10 press release, Matt Cowan, the CEO of Elite Sportswear, LP, the parent conglomerate of GK Elite expressed gratitude for the purposeful work put into crafting the 2024 uniforms.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1666, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R._Guy_Cowan\", \"score\": 0.9954871371898054, \"rank\": 0.004367429413443323, \"text\": \"Cowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso