any of the events or watching from home.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2343, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999319570657, \"rank\": 6.622514510990259e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Replicas\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"the eight leotards\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's final shirt\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2398}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All of Team USA will don head-to-toeRalph Lauren for the opening and closing ceremonies.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2430, \"end\": 2438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7733716620289844, \"rank\": 0.291009593445267, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toeRalph\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening and closing ceremonies\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, the brand revealed the planned ensembles for both men and women, including single-breasted wool blazers, oxford shirts, and classic tailored denim for opening festivities and moto-esque jackets, polo shirts, and white denim for closing celebrations.\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"the planned ensembles\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"both men\", \"from\": 2566, \